main event: Several observers, including a flight pilot and Braniff Airlines pilot, reported seeing a bright shiny object at England AFB in Louisiana on June 16, 1960.
interesting points: The object changed color from green to white and had an erratic flight path,It appeared to burn out with visible sparks from its body, The size of the object was described as being similar to a dime, Observations were made by multiple sources, including Air Force personnel and a civilian pilot, The incident was widely publicized by local radio and newspapers in Louisiana.
witness description: Various personnel including Air Force officers and a civilian airline pilot.
